quest.01DB719967817220.quest_desc.original:
The &dSupercritical Phase Shifter&r (&dSPS&r) is a large structure that uses as much power as you can give it to generate small amounts of &5Antimatter&r from large amounts of &bPolonium&r.

This completely eliminates all possible &cNuclear Waste&r if that is a concern, though the energy used to process an amount of &bPolonium&r is greater than the energy made to create it, so additional power is required.
{@pagebreak}
Simply feed chemical &bPolonium&r into one &dSPS Port&r, power into another attached to a &dSupercharged Coil&r on the inside, and one more &dSPS Port&r for extracting &5Antimatter&r.

Each 1000mB of &5Antimatter&r can be turned into a single &5Antimatter Pellet&r.

{image:ftb:textures/quests/mekanism/sps_supercritical.png width:100 height:100 align:center}

quest.01DB719967817220.quest_desc.translation:
大型結構&d超臨界移相器&r（&dSPS&r）消耗大量的&b釙&r來製造少量的&5反物質&r。

這個裝置完全消耗了任何可能出現的&c核廢料&r，唯一的問題是維持運轉所消耗的電力，會比製造&b釙&r產生的電力還多，因此還需要額外供應能量。
{@pagebreak}
需要三個&d超臨界移相器端口&r，一個端口輸入&b釙&r，另一個連接&d增壓線圈&r的端口輸入電力，最後一個端口用來輸出&5反物質&r。

每製造一顆&5反物質球&r需要 1000mb 的&5反物質&r。

{image:ftb:textures/quests/mekanism/sps_supercritical.png width:100 height:100 align:center}

quest.21322BAF061FE83F.quest_desc.original:
&6Neutronium&r gives you a start to work with, but now we will need to activate it. The &zNeutron Activator&r is a multiblock machine that will be used for this purpose.

This machine requires heat to simulate the power of the sun that is obviously missing in this stone world.
{@pagebreak}
It can convert &eNuclear Waste&r into &dPolonium&r, and &eLithium&r into &aTritium&r when powered with a single &6Neutron Pile&r.
{@pagebreak}
&eCustom Machinery&r has a built-in structure preview function that allows you to see where the blocks should be placed in the world.

To access this feature, simply click the Recipe arrow inside of the UI, then click the structure block in JEI to see the block placements in the world.

&7&oThe next page contains screenshots to help guide you, and the final page contains a screenshot of the fully-built structure. ->
{@pagebreak}
{image:ftb:textures/quests/neutron_activator/neutron_activator_ui.png width:200 height:90 align:center}

{image:ftb:textures/quests/neutron_activator/neutron_activator_jei.png width:180 height:150 align:center}
{@pagebreak}
The final structure should look like the picture below, with 2 Whisperglass on each of the four walls, the Reactor Reflector one up from the bottom-middle block, the Reactor Vent on top of that and the Empowered Void Block on the top-middle block.

{image:ftb:textures/quests/neutron_activator/neutron_activator_build.png width:120 height:150 align:center}

quest.21322BAF061FE83F.quest_desc.translation:
有了&6中子素&r是件好事，不過我們還要將其活化。&z中子活化器&r就是為此而生的多方塊機器。

&z中子活化器&r需要熱量來模擬太陽的能量，畢竟在這充滿石頭的世界顯然根本不存在什麼太陽。
{@pagebreak}
&z中子活化器&r利用活化的&6中子塵埃&r將&e核廢料&r轉換成&d釙&r，或將&e鋰&r轉換成&a氚&r。
{@pagebreak}
《&e自訂機器&r》內建結構預覽功能，能讓你查看方塊應該放置在世界中的哪個位置。

想要使用此功能，只需點擊介面中的配方箭頭，然後點擊 JEI 中的結構
方塊按鈕，即可查看方塊在世界中的擺放位置。

&7&o下一頁包含引導你的擷圖畫面，最後一頁則是已搭建好的結構圖。 ->
{@pagebreak}
{image:ftb:textures/quests/neutron_activator/neutron_activator_ui.png width:200 height:90 align:center}

{image:ftb:textures/quests/neutron_activator/zh_tw/neutron_activator_jei.png width:180 height:150 align:center}
{@pagebreak}
搭建完成的結構應該如下圖所示，四面牆壁上各有 2 個低語玻璃，

反應爐中子反射器位於底部中間方塊的正上方，

反應爐散熱器位於其上方，而充能煤晶方塊則位於頂部中間。

{image:ftb:textures/quests/neutron_activator/neutron_activator_build.png width:120 height:150 align:center}
